<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Fisker Inc. is an electric-vehicle company. It=
 went public by merging with a special purpose acquisition company in 2020,=
 back in the electric-vehicle-SPAC boom; its stock got as high as $28.50 pe=
r share (a market capitalization of about $7.9 billion) in 2021 but closed =
yesterday at $6.55 ($2.2 billion). It =E2=80=9Chas yet to generate <a href=
=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/32129843.264407/aHR0cHM6L=
y93d3cuc2VjLmdvdi9peD9kb2M9L0FyY2hpdmVzL2VkZ2FyL2RhdGEvMDAwMTcyMDk5MC8wMDAx=
NzIwOTkwMjMwMDAwNTIvZnNyLTIwMjMwMzMxLmh0bSNpZDdjYTAyOTU4MTZiNDIzYTllYmJlNDF=
lODNmMDk5NDNfMTY/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBb817b8b4" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" =
itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-dec=
oration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #0=
00000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> any significan=
t revenue</a> from its core business operations,=E2=80=9D lost about $547 m=
illion last year and =E2=80=9Cexpects to continue to incur significant oper=
ating losses for the foreseeable future.=E2=80=9D=C2=A0It had $652 million =
of cash as of March 31.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">People love electric-vehicle stocks, or at lea=
st they used to, so Fisker tops up its cash by selling stock. Last year it =
announced an <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/32129=
843.264407/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2VjLmdvdi9BcmNoaXZlcy9lZGdhci9kYXRhLzE3MjA5OTAv=
MDAwMTE5MzEyNTIyMTU4MDQwL2QzMzc0MTdkNDI0YjUuaHRt/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBa=
1195a80" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" s=
tyle=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-wid=
th: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; backgrou=
nd-color: #ccc;"> at-the-market offering</a> in which it would sell up to $=
350 million of stock, on the stock exchange, at market prices; it <a href=
=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/32129843.264407/aHR0cHM6L=
y93d3cuc2VjLmdvdi9peD9kb2M9L0FyY2hpdmVzL2VkZ2FyL2RhdGEvMDAwMTcyMDk5MC8wMDAx=
NzIwOTkwMjMwMDAwODQvZnNyLTIwMjMwNzEyLmh0bQ/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBdc7428d=
4" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=
=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: =
1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-c=
olor: #ccc;"> terminated that offering</a> last week after selling about $3=
27 million of stock. It replaced that plan with a new, far more complicated=
 plan to sell between $340 million and $680 million worth of stock. (Here i=
s <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/32129843.264407/=
aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2VjLmdvdi9peD9kb2M9L0FyY2hpdmVzL2VkZ2FyL2RhdGEvMDAwMTcyMDk=
5MC8wMDAxMTkzMTI1MjMxODQyMjcvZDUwMDUyMmQ4ay5odG0/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cC8=
f933118" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" s=
tyle=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-wid=
th: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; backgrou=
nd-color: #ccc;"> the 8-K</a> announcing this plan, and here is=C2=A0<a hre=
f=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/32129843.264407/aHR0cHM6=
Ly93d3cuc2VjLmdvdi9BcmNoaXZlcy9lZGdhci9kYXRhLzE3MjA5OTAvMDAwMTE5MzEyNTIzMTg=
0NzY4L2Q0OTk4MTVkNDI0YjUuaHRt/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBe700e8c4" itemprop=
=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #0=
