<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">If you are a big sovereign wealth fund, privat=
e equity firms will call you up a lot to ask you to invest in their new fun=
d. =E2=80=9CGive us $1 billion,=E2=80=9D they will say, =E2=80=9Cand we wil=
l invest it in the deals we pick and charge you a 2% fee plus 20% of profit=
s.=E2=80=9D And you might counter: =E2=80=9CNo, you go pick the deals and b=
ring them to us, and if we like them we will invest in them, and if we don=
=E2=80=99t we won=E2=80=99t, and either way we won=E2=80=99t pay you a fee.=
=E2=80=9D And then you=E2=80=99ll <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbus=
iness.com/click/32129843.264407/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2F=
